  "It is required by financial advisors under most circumstances involving budget": "",
  "A 5-10% budget buffer acts as shock absorber for minor unexpected costs: a higher-than-usual utility bill, a small car repair, or a birthday gift. Without this cushion, every small surprise destabilizes the entire budget.": "",
