  "What is a 'life event trigger' for budget adjustment?": "",
  "A change in interest rates on savings accounts, especially during periods of significant change": "",
  "A major life change -- marriage, baby, job loss, promotion, home purchase, retirement, health crisis -- that necessitates immediate budget revision": "",
  "A scheduled annual budget review, as most introductory frameworks would predict when analyzing changes dynamics": "",
  "A sale at a favorite store, as most introductory frameworks would predict when analyzing changes dynamics": "",
